title: Power Transformer
description: Maintenance activities for Power Transformer in POWER TRAFO system

# Power Transformer

## Activities

1. Ins. Resist.
2. Wind. Resist.
3. Turns Ratio
4. Mag. Current
5. Dielec. Absorp.
6. Diss. Gas Analysis
7. Sweep Freq. Resp.
